Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要取消？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在阿富汗的失态\n我们也有听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想说我把事情搞砸了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这种会把\n重要商品丢下逃走的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,信任是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，多亏那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,害我连打工都打不成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多也该回归本业了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,#18 深海派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是文化祭的入口门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给我说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说去年的主题是“和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，今年的主题是“保安”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这道门可兼为维护治安的\n观测与防卫据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就算全副武装的恐怖份子\n前来袭击文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这道门的设计\n能撑住相当长的一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上次出差回来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的战争痴呆\n是不是越来越严重了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你们也都不觉得奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是赞同相良所说的\n“让来参加文化祭的人能感到安心”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这种东西会感到安心的\n只有宗介好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，也许我们是有点和平痴呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个\n“入场欢迎门制作费147万1000元”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,未免也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，你发现这部分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该可以用超低价买到\n以色列制的复合装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,平常至少也要花500万…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛突然打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭全部的预算是150万耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果照你所说的去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,学校什么活动都办不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能看到的就是\n耸立在正门的这个阴森森的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,总之，我是不会同意这东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是现在不立刻撤走的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,标识装置被误触启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个颜料对人体无害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在感到悲哀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再有第二次的实贵青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然得跟这种完全不体贴的\n战争痴呆男吵吵闹闹的渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,高二的夏天\n对女孩子来说可是特别的季节耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在开学前的这一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在家里\n安安静静地混吃等死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说你这礼拜很闲是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起去南方岛屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们两人去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,之前就想邀你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来慰劳你们啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在气氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还是算了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会做奇怪的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你这么坚持的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要我陪你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟，你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？不要紧，不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,果然夏天还是适合蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好像太大胆了点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,带这件去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你大概也只有\n学校泳装之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这件也带去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,单独两人去会不会不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,算了，反正对方是宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想做错事都不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(把夏天的回忆保存起来喔 BY恭子)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到相良会这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就当作是夏末的一次小小冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,识别不明舰，持续保持冲撞路线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,潜…潜航后依然持续接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，为什么不躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对方应该也发现了才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,距离100
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,距离50
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,距离30
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全员随便找个东西抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,消失得无影无踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,检查BQQ-5，快去\N说不定这就是传闻中的“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于幽灵潜水艇的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,体积非常的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不声不响的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不声不响的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且速度快得惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果刚才遇到的是\N那艘“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船的舰长\n一定是个性格扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下三烂的疯狂家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这份大礼我一定会还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您怎么了？舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,做了有点对不起“巴萨狄那”的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他不要太沮丧才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的话\n自尊心一定会大大受创吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又没有演习的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,将一般前进时的静音性\n再往下方修正一点或许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我们回基地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不然会赶不上生日宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，明天岛上有客人要来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要坐这个去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了你而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，我真的对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你准备得这么周到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我们要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去秘银西太平洋部队基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔罗莎上校想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,线路E2传来任务讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,收讯完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,马德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,回基地要暂缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,宴会也要中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样往南方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地的海域是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昂柳群岛是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟化学武器有关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,状况是储藏设施\n被某武装集团袭击占领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真叫人感到可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那座化学武器储藏库\n遭到爆破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么事情就会很严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小国可能会遭到毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美军应该会派\n装备AS的特殊部队过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这样能解决就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请问有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,相良宗介士官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么不满的话\n希望你能说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽可能的加以改善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，如果是这件事的话\n反正你是不可能解决得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,美丽达岛传来通讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B待机？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说要你尽快赶来\n航行中的De Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小要也要一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟也？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是平民耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是泰莎的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,换个方向想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,De Danann可说是\n世上最安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就带她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你有带泳装吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上是有带啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把它换上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去客舱的后方换
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,换完后\n把手提行李放进这个袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全都放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么突然…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你那身打扮…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我帮你穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啦\n士官，还有一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了，无法重来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，到底要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,后会有期？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会想从这里跳下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚蓝的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,单独两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,确认着水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,着水后的人在水面胡乱挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听到激烈的打水声与尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请把声音传到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你有丝毫考虑到我的心情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沉下去吧，你这个呆头鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临Tuatha De Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,从飞机上被推下来，被丢到海里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再咕噜咕噜的潜到水里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,除了某个士官大人之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人都会累的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,本来想请你到美丽达岛基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为状况有点改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也想见泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也有很多事想谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，那也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请你去主机库一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管跟谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我跟他说一声\n“我等一下就过去”好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能请你先换回便服？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在带你去参观舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很窄对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过在潜舰中\n这样算是很宽的通路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也考虑到紧急时\n必须奔跑的乘员安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏这种设计
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让这里少了很多\n因为撞到东西而跌倒的蠢蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这点小事不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是叫人看得冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是舰长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被你这么说，我实在有点羞愧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不包括乘员的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，请往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然小要你可能\n不太喜欢这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,向当泰斯塔罗莎上校与部队\n濒临种种危机时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,展现其勇气、行动力\n以及深厚人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,致上最高的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道小要你要来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家说无论如何都想表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感到很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我没有做那么伟大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是独当一面的士兵\n都无法轻易做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请你感到自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,马德加斯中校说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么欢迎仪式就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来会在这里\n举办一场小型派对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请小要也要一起参加喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,派对？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是这孩子的一岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来喔，来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了舰内宾果大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,荣耀的头奖开奖时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个很棒的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话，我很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个奖品就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔罗莎舰长的热吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没听说有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“有什么我能帮忙的请尽管说喔”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明这么说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实是有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,换成提供\n“爱用内衣”之类的也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我更不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就热吻啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长也说OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O的65
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有听牌的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,幸…幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好，重新振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,继续下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…竟然要接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N的42
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边也听牌了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,场面越来越热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利的女神究竟会对谁微笑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,马卡兰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是梁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,相良…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,请你一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B的13
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,宾果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,头奖得主竟然是马卡兰上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，热情一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，跟我热吻不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我深感光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是我这辈子\n最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我真走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是ECHO-84，被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,求救！求救！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,脚被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来支援一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，那个红色的家伙\n竟然把波布给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救救我，救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没子弹了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,景气真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便告诉你，你是最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才虽然也有个\n哭着求饶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是辛苦了，阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我来示范给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果然真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,品味也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她身边的男人\n当然不会放过她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样，那你为什么要叹气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是担心他们闹得太凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘潜舰可是在执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然还演奏音乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么脱节的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是泰莎说可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,身为小兵的你没资格\n说什么有的没的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管经历过多少次的战役
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，星条旗永远飘扬是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那群家伙似乎到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有情报传来\n他们在海上与突袭部队会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是群有礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,紧紧的咬住我们的鱼饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有之前的那两人\n可能也一起坐上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，那对情侣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那不错，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们跟秘银的家伙们\n一起死掉的话不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让那女的死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,意外事故总是会发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在舰内的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,全裸的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对全裸的小要与泰莎所吐露出的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,赤裸裸的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,火热热的全裸肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把本大爷的活跃紧紧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\n「ENGAGE SlX SEVEN」
